data.description: Gorgeous Executive Home located on 1.36 acres in highly sought after Quail Crossing and NO HOA! Main level features formal dining room, office with glass doors and living room with built-ins and tons of natural light with amazing views.  Eat-in Kitchen has large kitchen island, gas stove and access to living room and dining room.  Upstairs boasts master suite with sitting room, dual vanities, walk in closet, separate shower and soaking tub.  Three additional bedrooms and full bathroom with double vanities.  Off the kitchen is private staircase leading to oversized private loft.  Screened patio and NEW deck overlooks the expansive backyard with private woods views.  Beautiful front porch is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee and/or entertaining.  Quail Crossing is boutique neighborhood with expansive private lots and located close to shopping, schools and outdoor activities!
